Blacknightmare::

She smiled back to Orchestra while she lead him to his quarters "We 
have several enemies..." she said "Our computers detected two 
annoying bots outside our base, some of us are attacking them; 
currently we have a battle in Space, Darkfate is choosing who will 
go..." looking Orchestra's eyes, Blacknightmare added "Are you 
impatient to go out and fight awhile, aren't you???"

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "dcoburn" <dcoburn@n...> wrote:
> ::Orchestra/Composer::
> 
>          Orchestra smiled back to Blacknightmare and followed.  He 
smiled at the way she had said "your" base.  It made him feel like he 
was actually a part of something.  
> 
>           "Tell me, Blacknightmare, who exactly are your enemies so 
far?  Like, your faction's, not personally.  I'd love to kick some 
butt in the name of the Predacons!" He said.
